  "shotList": "1) AtoG MS Looking down over the offshore oil rig, with a large barge secured to the rig. VG2) AtoG MS Oil rig and barge out in the open water; platform is around the oil rig; PAN back off the port quarter of barge. G3) AtoG CU PAN Past the oil rig out in water; PAN in close around the platfrom being built around the rig for working space. G4) AtoG MCU PAN In around the offshore oil rig; smaller platform is in in the water next to oil rig; small boat is alongside the oil rig in left FG. VG5) CU Oil worker, working with the oil rig. G6) MCU Oil workers setting a pipe down into a hole on the oil rig. G",
